I. Module: FriendlyHello
A. Purpose: Say hello using natural sentences
B. Inputs
   1. name: text
C. Outputs
   1. message: text
D. Flow
   1. kindly ask the user for name, fallback "World".
   2. set message to "Hello, " plus name plus "!".
   3. return message.
E. Tests
   1. input: name = Ada
   2. expectedOutput: Hello, Ada!
   3. input: {}
   4. expectedOutput: Hello, World!
F. Version: 0.2
